{"type":"message","id":"fca977d2","parentId":"18d2e96f","timestamp":"2026-04-13T10:26:50.398Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"用户问我从哪里找到 cron 设定方法的。我需要回顾刚才的对话记录，说明我是通过 `openclaw cron --help` 和 `openclaw cron add --help` 这些命令来获取帮助信息的。我应该诚实地告知用户我是通过具体命令来获取的。\n</think>\n\n仆查之之法有二：\n\n**其一：** 接阁命时，仆询彼有何时务之约无。以 `openclaw cron --help` 观之，得“可设时务”之能。\n\n**其二：** 仆遂行 `openclaw cron add --help` 以求其详，得诸段：\n\n```\nOptions:\n  --at <duration>     Run at specific time or duration (e.g. 20m)\n  --message <text>    Agent message payload\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --wake <mode>       Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")\n```\n\n示仆者，今时可于两翼择一而用之以告阁下。故仆以：\n```bash\nopenclaw cron add --at \"20m\" --system-event \"...\"\n```\n之策设定时。\n\n诸法如履平地，阁下可常以 `openclaw cron --help` 览之，观其能。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"vllm","model":"qwen3.5-9b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776075997088,"responseId":"chatcmpl-87732afd1216119e"}}
